    I purchased this to run my pool pump which is a 15amp circuit. I used this on a 12/3 extension cord and it will overheat. I installed this on the plug end as well as in the power supplying plug and still had overheating issues with it turning off. Since it continued to shut down, it serves no use to me for the intended reason I purchased it and it became a waste of money. Now if you have a pool pump that runs off way less amperage than it is rated for it may be a great item.
